!! Thread reply draft

Multi-tiddler context via parent hierarchy: the `thread` template walks the tagging chain to reconstruct a conversation. The reply is created as a new child tiddler with `author: llm-draft`.

''Settings covered:'' action mode, multi-tiddler context (parent hierarchy), `output-mode: text`, `output-target: new-tiddler`, `output-fields`, widget attribute precedence

!!! Setup

# Create a discussion root tiddler
# Tag reply tiddlers with the root and add an `author` field
# Invoke from the root tiddler

```
<$button>
  Draft reply
  <$llm-action
    tiddler=<<currentTiddler>>
    prompt="Based on this discussion thread, draft a thoughtful reply that addresses the latest points raised. Keep a professional but conversational tone."
    contextTemplate="$:/plugins/rimir/llm-connect/context-templates/thread"
  />
</$button>
```

